text: Kasper Lehikoinen (born 20 April 1992) is a Finnish badminton player. Trained at the BC Blue, he won bronze medals at the European Junior Badminton Championships in 2009 and 2011. == Achievements == === European Junior Championships === Boys' singles {| class="sortable wikitable" style="font- size: 90%;" !
